// Based on Harper Engine Whitepapers:
// - WP-072: Hardware Ray Tracing Fundamentals
// - WP-073: Acceleration Structure Building
// - WP-074: Ray Generation and Intersection
// - WP-075: RT Shadows and Ambient Occlusion
// - WP-076: RT Reflections and Refractions
// - WP-077: RT Global Illumination
// - WP-078: Hybrid Rasterization-RT Pipeline
